Retrieve List of Message Codes

get

/services/{version}/oggerr

Retrieve all message codes from the Oracle GoldenGate deployment.

Request

Path Parameters
  • version: string

    Oracle GoldenGate Service API version.

    Allowed Values: [ "v2" ]

Response

Supported Media Types
  • application/json

200 Response

All codes messages known to the Oracle GoldenGate deployment are retrieved.

Body ()
Root Schema : Oracle GoldenGate Collection
Type: object
Title: Oracle GoldenGate Collection
